lead_paragraph: LONDON (Reuters) – - Argentina will host Australia at Twickenham in their Rugby Championship match on Oct. 8, moving the southern hemisphere competition over the equator for the first time, its organisers said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Argentina to Host Australia at Twickenham
